{"tid":1969624,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"峻瀅兩房戶減價22萬元728萬易主　原業主賺兩球離場","createTime":"2020-04-12T14:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T06:26:44.000Z","uid":267488,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b437b35ad6328087ec95fcda0b61cd14333dbf5c","tid":1969624,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T14:06:54.000Z","msg":"利嘉閣地產分行高級聯席董事徐浩煇表示，該行新近促成將軍澳峻瀅1期7座高層C室成交，單位實用面積約499方呎，建築面積約659方呎，兩房間隔，望山景。單位於今年3月底月開始放盤，原業主開價750萬港元，經議價後減價22萬元或約2.9%，終以728萬元成功沽出，折合實用面積呎價約14,589元，折合建築面積呎價約11,047元。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，原業主於2016年9月以約528萬元購入上述單位，現轉手帳面獲利約200萬元，物業升值約38%。<br />\n<br />\n原業主獲利約200萬元<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ac3ffad539ef003e691785d4296a1dd5a505c7","tid":1969624,"uid":240670,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:15:22.000Z","msg":"賺少左已經世界末日<br />\n<br />\n原本轉手要賺500萬架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c3ec3ab9fac00fe75984f6d074270408fe8da4","tid":1969624,"uid":110988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T22:52:07.000Z","msg":"一入一出幾多開支, 借銀行又要息。你估佢袋哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f35e7ed30db2f3272294b26f93514c392b9393c","tid":1969624,"uid":104034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T23:47:44.000Z","msg":"起碼6.5m先買得過"},{"pid":"881358f9786f8325f4568906a4202715604471a9","tid":1969624,"uid":51105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8c3ec3ab9fac00fe75984f6d074270408fe8da4","tid":1969624,"uid":110988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T22:52:07.000Z","msg":"一入一出幾多開支, 借銀行又要息。你估佢袋哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" 